  <brief_title>Warfarin - How Good Are we at Maintaining Target Range ?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Observational Record Linkage Study Investigating Incidence of Adverse Events in Patients Anti-coagulated for Lone Atrial Fibrillation.</official_title>
